                <p class="text-center">
                    <small>Click map to place marker. Drag marker to move. <span class="pseudolink" id="removeMapMarker">Click here to delete marker</span>.</small>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-7 col-md-pull-5">

